Simple Process
Get help in 3 easy steps
Whether you need a one-time favor or ongoing help, Junior Job Hunt makes it simple to connect with a trusted local Tasker.
01

Post Your Task

Describe what you need â€” from lawn mowing to running errands. Include your location and timing preferences and submit your request in seconds.

02

Get Matched

We'll connect you with a nearby student Tasker who fits your needs. Every Tasker is screened and vetted before joining our platform.

03

Task Done!

Your Tasker shows up, gets the job done, and you pay a fair, affordable rate. You've helped a local student while getting your to-do list cleared.

Why Junior Job Hunt
Your satisfaction, guaranteed
We built Junior Job Hunt because we believe in community. Young people deserve flexible work opportunities â€” and neighbors deserve affordable, trustworthy help.

Safe Environment for Taskers

We vet the adults doing the hiring â€” not the kids. Every customer is reviewed before being matched with a Tasker so our young workers always have a safe, trusted environment to earn in.

Community First

Founded by two USD college students, we understand what local youth need. Your hire directly supports a young person building real-world skills.

Affordable Rates

Because Taskers are local students (not large companies), rates are fair for both sides â€” affordable for you, meaningful for them.

App Launching 2026

Our mobile app is on the way and launching in 2026 â€” making it even easier to hire a Tasker or pick up work in your neighborhood. For any questions or concerns reach us at [email protected]
